A.7 Validation and Refinement Protocol

A.7.1 Methodological Validation

Internal Validation Tests:

1. Consistency Test: Multiple teams generate blueprints for same problem
2. Replication Test: Same team regenerates blueprints after time delay
3. Expert Validation: Domain experts assess blueprint quality
4. Predictive Test: Blueprint predictions tested against new data

External Validation Benchmarks:

· Comparison with other theory generation methods
· Application to historical cases with known outcomes
· User satisfaction and effectiveness surveys
· Impact on subsequent research and practice

